{
  "texts": [
    "This shows the wide range of prompts used to give the context and requirements to the LLM for code generation.",
    "Analyzing the prompts qualitatively, we have categorized the prompts broadly into 5 categories.",
    "(1) Improve student-written code (correctness/code quality) (2) Simple tasks and help in C++ (3) Data structures for a specific requirement (4) Solutions/algorithms for common problems (5) Others Category (5) includes prompts to generate test cases, and design patterns as well as prompts to fill knowledge gaps.",
    "Table 4 shows the breakdown of prompts in each category along with some examples.",
    "We can see the most usage of AI code generation has been for simple tasks in C++ along with generating solutions/algorithms for specific problems."
  ]
}